      "note": "\"Their hearts\": the pronoun \"their\" refers to the angels nearest to Allah. On the Day of Judgement there will be such an irresistible manifestation of Power that even they will be silent for a while, and will scarcely realise what is happening. They will question each other, and only thus will they regain their bearings. Or \"their\" may refer to those who seek intercession."
